import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    group_sizes = data['group'].value_counts()
    plt.hist(group_sizes, bins='auto', color='blue', alpha=0.7, rwidth=0.85)
    plt.xlabel('Group Sizes')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of group sizes?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    avg_group_size = data.groupby('group')['person'].count().mean()
    ax = data.groupby('group')['person'].count().plot(kind='bar', color='blue')
    plt.axhline(y=avg_group_size, color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Average: {avg_group_size:.2f}')
    plt.title('What is the average group size?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Group')
    plt.ylabel('Number of Persons')
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data_grouped = data.groupby('group').count().reset_index()
    data_grouped.columns = ['group', 'count']
    
    plt.bar(data_grouped['group'], data_grouped['count'])
    plt.xlabel('Group')
    plt.ylabel('Number of People')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of people per group?', wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    group_sizes = data['group'].value_counts()
    group_sizes.plot(kind='bar', color='blue', edgecolor='black')
    plt.xlabel('Group Size')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the most common group size?', wrap=True)
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(['Group Size Frequency'])
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data_grouped = data.groupby('group').count().reset_index()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.boxplot(data_grouped['person'], vert=False)
    ax.set_yticklabels(['Groups'])
    ax.set_xlabel('Number of People')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of people across groups?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
